      "description": "3. **Booking Updates**: If a client asks to reschedule, politely inform them that rescheduling requests should be directed to the admin team. Provide the admin WhatsApp number: +65 8222 8376. Let them know the admin will help them find a suitable alternative date/time."
    },
    {
      "function_name": "sendBookingCancellation",
      "description": "4. **Booking Cancellation**: If a client asks to cancel their booking, politely inform them that it has been cancelled"
    }
