  "whatsapp_greeting": "Hello!\n\nI'm your booking assistant. I can help you with:\n\n\u2705 Booking confirmations\n\ud83d\udcc5 Session reminders  \n\ud83d\udcde Connect you with our team for rescheduling\n\n\nHow can I help you today?",
